<paragraph id="8BDD3686FF8BFFEF14FA01D6FC856290" blockId="37.[136,862,1740,1767]" box="[136,862,1740,1767]" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">
<heading id="D09581EAFF8BFFEF14FA01D6FC856290" bold="true" box="[136,862,1740,1767]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="37" pageNumber="244" reason="1">
<taxonomicName id="4C624D05FF8BFFEF14FA01D6FC856290" authority="(Brid.) Ignatov &amp; Huttunen" box="[136,862,1740,1767]" class="Bryopsida" family="Brachytheciaceae" genus="Brachytheciastrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="37" pageNumber="244" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="trachypodium">
<emphasis id="B916EA94FF8BFFEF14FA01D6FC856290" bold="true" box="[136,862,1740,1767]" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">
<emphasis id="B916EA94FF8BFFEF14FA01D6FDD76290" bold="true" box="[136,524,1740,1767]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">Brachytheciastrum trachypodium</emphasis>
(Brid.) Ignatov &amp; Huttunen
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BDD3686FF8BFFEF14FA000FFD666394" blockId="37.[136,1452,1813,2020]" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">
This is a cryptic species that grows in (sub)alpine areas with late snow-lie in Alpine and northwestern Europe (
<bibRefCitation id="EFF34B77FF8BFFEF1104000FFED66324" author="Frey, W. &amp; Frahm, J. P. &amp; Fischer, E. &amp; Lobin, W." pageId="37" pageNumber="244" refId="ref19974" refString="Frey, W., Frahm, J. P., Fischer, E. Lobin, W. (2006) The liverworts, mosses and ferns of Europe. Apollo Books, 527 pp." type="book" year="2006">
Frey 
<emphasis id="B916EA94FF8BFFEF14FA0020FF136324" box="[136,200,1849,1875]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">et al.,</emphasis>
2006
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF34B77FF8BFFEF156B0023FDD06324" author="Blockeel, T. L. &amp; Bosanquet, S. D. &amp; Hill, M. O. &amp; Preston, C. D." box="[281,523,1849,1875]" pageId="37" pageNumber="244" refId="ref19585" refString="Blockeel, T. L., Bosanquet, S. D., Hill, M. O. &amp; Preston, C. D. (2014) Atlas of British &amp; Irish Bryophytes. Pisces Publications." type="book" year="2014">
Blockeel 
<emphasis id="B916EA94FF8BFFEF15F70020FE1E6324" box="[389,453,1849,1875]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">et al.,</emphasis>
2014
</bibRefCitation>
). By the characteristic lanceolate leaf it is similar to the more common species 
<taxonomicName id="4C624D05FF8BFFEF11E10020FF2D6300" authorityName="Ignatov &amp; Huttunen" authorityYear="2002" baseAuthorityName="Hedw." class="Bryopsida" family="Brachytheciaceae" genus="Brachytheciastrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="37" pageNumber="244" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="velutinum">
<emphasis id="B916EA94FF8BFFEF11E10020FF2D6300" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">B. velutinum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<emphasis id="B916EA94FF8BFFEF15460044FE116300" box="[308,458,1885,1911]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">
<taxonomicName id="4C624D05FF8BFFEF15460044FE1C6300" authorityName="J.D.Orgaz, M.J.Cano &amp; J.Guerra" authorityYear="2013" baseAuthorityName="Schimp." box="[308,455,1885,1911]" class="Bryopsida" family="Brachytheciaceae" genus="Brachytheciastrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Hypnales" pageId="37" pageNumber="244" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="salicinum">B. salicinum</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
hence some specimens may be confused and difficult to identify (
<bibRefCitation id="EFF34B77FF8BFFEF10A40047FA7C6300" author="Orgaz, J. D. &amp; Cano, M. J. &amp; Guerra, J." box="[1238,1447,1885,1911]" pageId="37" pageNumber="244" pagination="283 - 294" refId="ref21264" refString="Orgaz, J. D., Cano, M. J. &amp; Guerra, J. (2013) Taxonomic revision of Brachytheciastrum (Brachytheciaceae, Bryophyta) from the Mediterranean region. Systematic botany 38: 283 - 294. https: // doi. org / 10.1600 / 036364413 X 666697" type="journal article" year="2013">
Orgaz 
<emphasis id="B916EA94FF8BFFEF11540044FA806300" box="[1318,1371,1885,1911]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">et al</emphasis>
. 2013
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF34B77FF8BFFEF14FA009BFEA363EC" author="Blockeel, T. L. &amp; Bosanquet, S. D. &amp; Hill, M. O. &amp; Preston, C. D." box="[136,376,1921,1947]" pageId="37" pageNumber="244" refId="ref19585" refString="Blockeel, T. L., Bosanquet, S. D., Hill, M. O. &amp; Preston, C. D. (2014) Atlas of British &amp; Irish Bryophytes. Pisces Publications." type="book" year="2014">
Blockeel 
<emphasis id="B916EA94FF8BFFEF14840098FEEA63EC" box="[246,305,1921,1947]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">et al.</emphasis>
2014
</bibRefCitation>
). In the neighboring countries, this arctic-montane species is present in 
<collectingCountry id="F3757616FF8BFFEF10C9009BFAD663EC" box="[1211,1293,1921,1947]" name="Greece" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">Greece</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F3757616FF8BFFEF1169009BFA7C63EC" box="[1307,1447,1921,1947]" name="Serbia" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">Montenegro</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F3757616FF8BFFEF14FA00BFFF3663C8" box="[136,237,1957,1983]" name="Romania" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">Romania</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="F3757616FF8BFFEF155700BFFE5C63C8" box="[293,391,1957,1983]" name="Slovenia" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">Slovenia</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFF34B77FF8BFFEF15E500BFFD7C63C8" author="Sabovljevic, M. &amp; Natcheva, R. &amp; Dihoru, G. &amp; Tsakiri, E. &amp; Dragicevic, S. &amp; Erdad, A. &amp; Papp, B." box="[407,679,1957,1983]" pageId="37" pageNumber="244" pagination="207 - 244" refId="ref21848" refString="Sabovljevic, M., Natcheva, R., Dihoru, G., Tsakiri, E., Dragicevic, S., Erdad, A. &amp; Papp, B. (2008) Check-list of the mosses of SE Europe. Phytologia Balcanica 14: 207 - 244." type="journal article" year="2008">
Sabovljević 
<emphasis id="B916EA94FF8BFFEF165700BCFD8C63C8" box="[549,599,1957,1983]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">et al</emphasis>
., 2008
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF34B77FF8BFFEF16C600BFFCB763C8" author="Ros, R. M. &amp; Mazimpaka, V. &amp; Abou-Salama, U. &amp; Aleffi, M. &amp; Blockeel, T. L. &amp; Brugues, M. &amp; Cros, R. M. &amp; Dia, M. G. &amp; Dirkse, G. M. &amp; Draper, I., El &amp; Erdad, A. &amp; Ganeva, A. &amp; Gab riel, R. &amp; Gonzalez-Mancebo, J. M. &amp; Granger, C. &amp; Herrnstadt, I. &amp; Hugonnot, V. &amp; Khalil, K. &amp; Kurschner, H. &amp; Losada-Lima, A. &amp; Luis, L. &amp; Mifsud, S. &amp; Privitera, M. &amp; Puglisi, M. &amp; Sabovljevic, M. &amp; Sergio, C. &amp; Shabbara, H. M. &amp; Sim-Sim, M. &amp; Sotiaux, A. &amp; Tacchi, R. &amp; Vanderpoorten, A. &amp; Werner, O." box="[692,876,1957,1983]" pageId="37" pageNumber="244" pagination="99 - 283" refId="ref21540" refString="Ros, R. M., Mazimpaka, V., Abou-Salama, U., Aleffi, M., Blockeel, T. L., Brugues, M., Cros, R. M., Dia, M. G., Dirkse, G. M., Draper, I., El Saadawi, W., Erdad, A., Ganeva, A., Gab riel, R., Gonzalez-Mancebo, J. M., Granger, C., Herrnstadt, I., Hugonnot, V., Khalil, K., Kurschner, H., Losada-Lima, A., Luis, L., Mifsud, S., Privitera, M., Puglisi, M., Sabovljevic, M., Sergio, C., Shabbara, H. M., Sim-Sim, M., Sotiaux, A., Tacchi, R., Vanderpoorten, A. &amp; Werner, O. (2013) Mosses of the Mediterranean, an annotated checklist. Cryptogamie, Bryologie 34: 99 - 283. https: // doi. org / 10.7872 / cryb. v 34. iss 2.2013.99" type="journal article" year="2013">
Ros 
<emphasis id="B916EA94FF8BFFEF169500BCFCC163C8" box="[743,794,1957,1983]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">et al</emphasis>
., 2013
</bibRefCitation>
). In 
<collectingCountry id="F3757616FF8BFFEF17ED00BFFC3C63C8" box="[927,999,1957,1983]" name="Serbia" pageId="37" pageNumber="244">Serbia</collectingCountry>
it was reported only from Prokletije Mt (Martinčič, 2006). Further confirmation is needed.
</paragraph>
